<emphasis id="EA54DB60C30145252E609F80E09F17A9" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">Sphinx achilleae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Esper, 1780, by subsequent designation, Holik, 1938, Entomologische Rundschau 55: 352. 
<emphasis id="FEDC4BA1086445F247A6413587002235" bold="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">Syn. rev.</emphasis>
